{"type": "article", "id": 26353, "title": "艺术羊毛毯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-04T07:19:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115800H7pwx1bCQZdaq5sj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">无论你之前见过多少条漂亮的毯子，当看到艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.alexkeha.com/\">Alexandra Kehayoglou</a> 制作的这些羊毛毯时或许还是会在心底惊呼一声“美如画”。采用回收材料手工制成的毯子每一块都是独一无二的，好像是在房间里放置了一个梦幻花园，给人一种沉浸式的体验。根据大小，艺术家需要经过一周甚至两个月才能制作完工。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021157587YAot1PH2DWlINa6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67395833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115758c8hP3lLoa4ZgOiUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021157592cWKDnpZtJdfgQyC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115759mn1j0W53gYaFSI7q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}